The paper focuses on federated learning for visual classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the challenges of data diversity and quality, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The development of new algorithms for resampling and reweighting also involves natural language processing techniques (cs.CL). Finally, the paper touches on the issue of privacy and security in distributed learning, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
